<!-- - [RFC #3553](https://github.com/rust-lang/rfcs/pull/3553) -->
<ul>
<li><a href="https://github.com/rust-lang/rfcs/pull/3371">RFC #3371: CARGO_TARGET_BASE_DIR</a></li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/rust-lang/rfcs/pull/3243">RFC #3243: Packages as optional namespaces</a></li>
